ADDIS ABABA, Ethiopia, February 12, 2019/APO Group/ --
                                                        
                            The United States, through the U.S. Agency for International Development (USAID), is announcing the launch of its new five year Health Financing Improvement Program to invest in expanding Ethiopia’s capacity to provide quality affordable healthcare to its citizens.  USAID Mission Director Leslie Reed and the Honorable State Minister of Health Dr. Lia Tadesse are expected to attend and deliver remarks.



The United States Embassy in Addis Ababa invites you to attend this event.

Date: February 14, 2019 at 8:30 a.m.

Venue: Hilton Hotel, Addis Ababa

To confirm attendance, please contact Communications and Knowledge Management Advisor under USAID’s Health Financing Improvement Program at ayenew_haileselassie@hfipethiopia.com .